2005年5月30日，年仅18岁的美国少女'''娜塔莉·安·霍洛威'''（{{lang-en|Natalee Ann Holloway}}）在[[荷兰王国|荷兰]]位于[[加勒比地区|加勒比地区]]岛屿[[阿鲁巴岛|阿鲁巴岛]]失踪，案件至今未破。霍洛威是[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]][[芒廷布鲁克_(阿拉巴马州)|芒廷布鲁克]]人士，于5月24日从[[芒廷布鲁克高中|芒廷布鲁克高中]]毕业，失踪时正在岛上旅游<ref name="USA Today 2005-06-02">{{cite news | last1 = Koch | first1 = Wendy | date = 2005-06-02 | title = Search continues in Aruba for missing teen | work = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150927222752/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/nation/2005-06-02-teen-aruba_x.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/nation/2005-06-02-teen-aruba_x.htm | archivedate = 2015-09-27 | publisher = Gannett }}</ref>。案件在美国引起媒体的极大关注<ref name="BBC News 2005-06-25">{{cite news | last = Davis | first = Matthew | date = 2005-06-25 | title = Missing teen case grips US media | publisher = [[BBC新闻|BBC News]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305154557/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/4125492.stm | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/4125492.stm | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

霍洛威原定于5月30日搭航班回国，但没有赶到机场登机<ref name="Court TV 2005-06-08">{{cite web | title = Judge: Both suspects can be held in Alabama teenager's disappearance in Aruba | date = 2005-06-08 | publisher = Court TV | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.courttv.com/news/2005/0608/aruba_ap.html | accessdate = 2009-01-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090109212931/http://www.courttv.com/news/2005/0608/aruba_ap.html | archivedate = 2009-01-09 }}</ref>。同学最后一次看到她是在[[奥拉涅斯塔德_(阿鲁巴)|奥拉涅斯塔德]]的[[卡洛斯和查理|卡洛斯和查理]]连锁餐馆暨夜总会门外<ref name="CNN 2005-06-09">{{cite news | title = Judge orders suspects held in teen's disappearance | date = 2005-06-09 | publisher = CNN | accessdate = 2008-03-22 | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2005/LAW/06/08/missing.teen/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20050901050823/http://edition.cnn.com/2005/LAW/06/08/missing.teen/ | archivedate = 2005-09-01 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，当时霍洛威上了当地居民[[约兰·范德斯洛特|约兰·范德斯洛特]]的车，车上还有迪帕克·卡尔珀和萨蒂什·卡尔珀兄弟俩。三人之后面对质询时都称他们只是送霍洛威回酒店，对她此后的去向一无所知<ref name="ABC News 2006-02-23">{{cite web |title=Dutch Teen Tells 'Primetime' About Night With Natalee Holloway |date=2006-02-23 |publisher=ABC News |accessdate=2012-10-05 |archivedate=2012-10-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121005061106/http://abclocal.go.com/kgo/story?section=news%2Fnational_world&id=3935503 |url=http://abclocal.go.com/kgo/story?section=news/national_world&id=3935503 }}</ref>。有关部门经进一步调查先后两次逮捕范德斯洛特、三次逮捕卡尔珀兄弟，怀疑他们同失踪案有关。但由于缺乏证据，三人都未经起诉获释。<ref name="CNN 2006-05-31">{{cite news | last = O'Neill | first = Ann | date = 2006-05-31 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160419114119/http://edition.cnn.com/2006/LAW/05/30/aruba.mystery/ | title = Holloway case a mystery after a year of 'catch and release' | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2006/LAW/05/30/aruba.mystery/ | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | publisher = [[CNN|CNN]] | archivedate = 2016-04-19 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="AP 2007-11-22, 3 re-arrested">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | date = 2007-11-22 | title = Three Young Men Re-Arrested in Natalee Holloway Disappearance | publisher = [[福克斯新闻频道|Fox News Channel]] | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306182730/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2007/11/22/three-young-men-re-arrested-in-natalee-holloway-disappearance.html | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2007/11/22/three-young-men-re-arrested-in-natalee-holloway-disappearance.html }}</ref>

在数百名志愿者帮助下，阿鲁巴的侦察人员开展大规模搜索行动寻找霍洛威。[[联邦调查局|联邦调查局]]派出多名特工参与搜救，<ref name="LA Times 2007-06-04">{{cite news | last = Williams | first = Carol | date = 2007-06-04 | title = In Holloway case, Aruba also suffers | newspaper = [[洛杉矶时报|Los Angeles Times]] | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160414020550/http://www.latimes.com/travel/la-trw-aruba4jun4-story.html | archivedate = 2016-04-14 | url = http://www.latimes.com/travel/la-trw-aruba4jun4-story.html | quote = [...] when locals mutter about American media distortions and 'missing white woman syndrome'. }}</ref>另有50名[[荷兰皇家陆军|荷兰军人]]及三架拥有特别配备的[[荷兰皇家空军|荷兰空军]][[F-16战隼战斗机|F-16战隼战斗机]]加入<ref name="MSNBC 2005-06-06">{{cite web | last = Savidge | first = Martin | date = 2005-06-06 | title = Aruba gripped by mystery over missing teen | publisher = MSNBC | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/8118094/ | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306080758/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/8118094/ }}</ref><ref name="AP 2007-11-22, F16">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | date = 2007-11-22 | title = Judge Approves Transfer for Suspect in Natalee Holloway Disappearance Case | publisher = Fox News Channel | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307024132/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2007/11/22/judge-approves-transfer-for-suspect-in-natalee-holloway-disappearance-case.html | archivedate = 2016-03-07 | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2007/11/22/judge-approves-transfer-for-suspect-in-natalee-holloway-disappearance-case.html }}</ref><ref name="demonstration">{{cite web | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/8484217/ | title = Some Arubans angry at Holloway's mom | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | date = 2005-06-06 | publisher = MSNBC | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308133640/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/8484217/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。除地面搜索外，还有多名潜水员下海寻找霍洛威的尸体<ref name="divers">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307094226/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/aruba-divers-find-nothing/ | archivedate = 2016-03-07 | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/aruba-divers-find-nothing/ | title = Aruba divers find nothing | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | date = 2005-08-29 | publisher = CBS News }}</ref>，但始终一无所获<ref name="MSNBC 2006-05-23">{{cite web | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/11100850/ns/world_news-americas/t/holloway-suspect-released-detention/ | title = Holloway suspect released from detention | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | date = 2006-05-23 | publisher = MSNBC | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313025455/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/11100850/ns/world_news-americas/t/holloway-suspect-released-detention/ | archivedate = 2016-03-13 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="Alcohol">{{cite web | date = 2006-03-24 | publisher = Court TV | url = http://www.courttv.com/news/holloway/032406_ap.html | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090109175245/http://www.courttv.com/news/holloway/032406_ap.html | archivedate = 2009-01-09 | title = Police: Natalee Holloway may have died from alcohol, drugs | accessdate = 2009-01-09 }}</ref><ref name="Rawls 2012-01-12">{{cite news | last = Rawls | first = Phillip | date = 2012-01-12 | title = Missing teenager Natalee Holloway declared dead | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = [[赫芬顿邮报|Huffington Post]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304211247/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/huff-wires/20120112/us-missing-teen-aruba/ | url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/huff-wires/20120112/us-missing-teen-aruba/ | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。2007年12月18日，阿鲁巴检察机关宣布结案，不会起诉任何嫌疑人<ref name="Fox News 2007-12-19">{{cite news | title = Aruba Prosecutors End Investigation into Disappearance of American Teen Natalee Holloway | date = 2007-12-19 | publisher = Fox News Channel | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305161624/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2007/12/19/aruba-investigation-into-disappearance-american-teen-natalee-holloway-is-not.html | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2007/12/19/aruba-investigation-into-disappearance-american-teen-natalee-holloway-is-not.html }}</ref><ref name="USA Today 2007-12-18">{{cite news | title = Aruba prosecutors close Holloway case | date = 2007-12-18 | work = USA Today | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | archivedate = 2016-05-07 | deadurl = no | publisher = Gannett | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160507170450/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/world/2007-12-18-holloway-case-closed_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/world/2007-12-18-holloway-case-closed_N.htm }}</ref>。2008年2月1日，阿鲁巴检察机关在获得约兰·范德斯洛特认罪的视频片段后宣布恢复案件调查取证工作，据这段录像显示，范德斯洛特在吸食[[大麻|大麻]]后声称霍洛威已于2005年5月30日早上死亡，尸体是由他的某个朋友帮忙处理掉<ref name="ABC News 2008-02-03">{{cite web | last1 = James | first1 = Michael S. | last2 = Cuomo | first2 = Chris | last3 = Velmans | first3 = Jissica | date = 2008-02-03 | title = Holloway Suspect: 'I Know What Happened' | publisher = ABC News | url = http://abcnews.go.com/TheLaw/Story?id=4222253 | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303172924/http://abcnews.go.com/TheLaw/Story?id=4222253 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 }}</ref>。范德斯洛特之后否认自己在视频中的说法属实，之后又在接受[[格蕾塔·范叙斯特伦|格蕾塔·范叙斯特伦]]采访时称已把霍洛威当[[性奴隶|性奴隶]]卖掉，此后又再度否认这一说法的真实性<ref name="Fox News 2008-11-24">{{cite news | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2008/11/25/joran-van-der-sloot-goes-on-record-with-new-natalee-holloway-story.html | title = Joran van der Sloot goes 'On the Record' with new Natalee Holloway story | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305155712/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2008/11/25/joran-van-der-sloot-goes-on-record-with-new-natalee-holloway-story.html | date = 2008-11-24 | publisher = WTVY | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

霍洛威的双亲批评阿鲁巴警方在案件调查及质询最后看到他们女儿的三名男子期间工作有欠严谨，还呼吁[[杯葛|抵制]]阿鲁巴并得到[[阿拉巴马州州长|阿拉巴马州州长]][[鲍勃·赖利|鲍勃·赖利]]支持，但没有获得联邦层面的支持<ref name="USA Today 2005-11-21">{{cite news | title = Poll: Most Alabama residents support Aruba boycott | date = 2005-11-21 | work = USA Today | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/travel/news/2005-11-21-aruba-boycott_x.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121102120938/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/travel/news/2005-11-21-aruba-boycott_x.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2012-11-02 }}</ref><ref name="NatSupport">{{cite news | title = Washington refuses to back Aruba boycott | url = http://www.expatica.com/nl/news/Washington-refuses-to-back-Aruba-boycott_133671.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160601143407/http://www.expatica.com/nl/news/Washington-refuses-to-back-Aruba-boycott_133671.html | date = 2005-11-10 | publisher = Expatica | archivedate = 2016-06-01 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-06-01 }}</ref>。2012年1月12日，阿拉巴马州法官宣告娜塔莉·安·霍洛威在法律上已经死亡<ref>{{cite news | title = Natalee Holloway declared dead by judge six years after disappearance | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | location = London | date = 2012-01-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150701141015/http://www.theguardian.com/world/2012/jan/12/natalee-holloway-declared-legally-dead | url = http://www.theguardian.com/world/2012/jan/12/natalee-holloway-declared-legally-dead | work = [[卫报|The Guardian]] | archivedate = 2015-07-01 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
