娜塔莉·安·霍洛威于1986年10月21日在美国[[密西西比州|密西西比州]][[海恩兹县_(密西西比州)|海恩兹县]]的克林顿（{{lang|en|Clinton}}）出生，是父亲大卫·爱德华·“戴夫”·霍洛威（{{lang|en|David Edward "Dave" Holloway}}）和母亲伊丽莎白·安·雷诺兹·“贝丝”·霍洛威（{{lang|en|Elizabeth Ann Reynolds "Beth" Holloway}}）的第一个孩子<ref name="AP 2006-04-25" />。1993年父母离异后，霍洛威和弟弟马修（{{lang|en|Matthew}}）由母亲带大。2000年，伊丽莎白再婚，嫁给阿拉巴马州知名商人乔治·“尤格”·特威蒂（{{lang|en|George "Jug" Twitty}}），娜塔莉因此迁居[[芒廷布鲁克|芒廷布鲁克]]<ref name="DHolloway 2006, ch. Everybody's Child / Aruba">{{cite book | last1 = Holloway | first1 = Dave | first2 = R. Stephanie | last2 = Good | first3 = Larry | last3 = Garrison | date = 2006-04 | title = Aruba: The Tragic Untold Story of Natalee Holloway and Corruption in Paradise | url = https://archive.org/details/arubatragicuntol0000holl | publisher = Thomas Nelson | location = Nashville, TN | isbn = 978-1-59555-063-7 | oclc = 63472537 | chapter = Everybody's Child / Aruba}}</ref>。娜塔莉以优异成绩从芒廷布鲁克高中毕业，是[[美国国家荣誉协会|国家荣誉协会]]成员，曾参加校[[舞队|舞队]]及其它多项课外活动<ref name="dependable">{{cite web | url = http://www.courttv.com/news/2005/0606/aruba_ap.html | archivedate = 2009-04-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090409004826/http://www.courttv.com/news/2005/0606/aruba_ap.html | deadurl = yes | title = Ala. girl missing in Aruba called 'dependable' by friends | accessdate = 2009-04-09 | date = 2005-06-06 | publisher = Court TV }}</ref><ref name="reward">{{cite news | title = Family increases reward for missing U.S. teen in Aruba | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/nation/2005-07-21-holloway-reward-increased_x.htm | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | date = 2005-07-21 | work = USA Today | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-05-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160507155336/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/nation/2005-07-21-holloway-reward-increased_x.htm | publisher = Gannett }}</ref>。她还获得就读[[阿拉巴马大学|阿拉巴马大学]]的全额奖学金<ref name="HansenSearch">{{cite web | last = Hansen | first = Chris | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/23301056/page/2/ | title = The search for Natalee Holloway | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305131810/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/23301056/page/2/ | date = 2008-02-22 | publisher = NBC News | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，计划在该校攻读医学预科课程<ref name="ABC News 2005–06-08">{{cite news | url = http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/story?id=829682&page=1 | title = Missing teen's family still has hope | date = 2005-06-08 | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | publisher = American Broadcast Corporation | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304085849/http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/story?id=829682&page=1 | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。女儿失踪时，戴夫·霍洛威是密西西比州[[劳德代尔县_(密西西比州)|劳德代尔县]]县城[[默里迪恩_(密西西比州)|默里迪恩]]（{{lang|en|Meridian}}）[[州立农业保险公司|州立农业保险公司]]的保险代理人，贝丝·特威蒂则在[[芒廷布鲁克学校系统|芒廷布鲁克学校系统]]工作<ref name="DHolloway 2006, ch. Everybody's Child / Aruba" /><ref name="State Farm Dave Holloway">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308042014/https://www.statefarm.com/agent/US/MS/Meridian/Dave-Holloway-DQ2XH1YS000 | url = https://www.statefarm.com/agent/US/MS/Meridian/Dave-Holloway-DQ2XH1YS000 | title = Dave Holloway Insurance Agency | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | publisher = State Farm | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="CNN 2005-08-18">{{cite news | url = http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0508/18/lkl.01.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306210012/http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0508/18/lkl.01.html | deadurl = no | title = Interview With Beth Holloway Twitty; BTK Sentenced | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | date = 2005-08-18 | publisher = Larry King Live | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。

== 失踪 ==
霍洛威于2005年5月24日从位于阿拉巴马州[[伯明翰_(阿拉巴马州)|伯明翰]]富裕郊区的芒廷布鲁克高中毕业<ref name="USA Today 2005-06-02" />，并于5月26日同124名同学一起抵达[[阿鲁巴|阿鲁巴]]，开始为期五天的非正式毕业旅行<ref name="dependable" /><ref name="Court TV 2005-06-07">{{cite web | title = Alabama town hopes for safe return of missing teen | date = 2005-06-07 | publisher = Court TV | url = http://www.courttv.com/news/2005/0607/missingteen_ap.html | accessdate = 2007-05-12 | archivedate = 2009-01-09 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090109210743/http://www.courttv.com/news/2005/0607/missingteen_ap.html }}</ref>。共有七名成年人陪同这些学生<ref name="Vanity" />，据随行教师鲍勃·普拉默（{{lang|en|Bob Plummer}}）所述，陪同人员每天都会同众学子见面，确保事情没有差池<ref name="Fox News 2006-02-24">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306195118/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/02/24/transcript-holloway-chaperone-speaks-out.html | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/02/24/transcript-holloway-chaperone-speaks-out.html | title = Transcript: Holloway Chaperone Speaks Out | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | date = 2006-02-24 | publisher = On the Record | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。另据组织此次旅行的乔迪·比尔曼（{{lang|en|Jodi Bearman}}）表示，陪同人员并不需要随时掌握所有学生的一举一动<ref name="Vanity">{{cite web | url = http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2006/01/natalee200601 | title = Missing Missing White Female | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160412205819/http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2006/01/natalee200601 | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | last = Burrough | first = Bryan | date = 2006-01 | work = Vanity Fair | archivedate = 2016-04-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref name="FNCThree">{{cite news | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306182724/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/06/18/three-aruba-suspects-going-to-prison.html | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/06/18/three-aruba-suspects-going-to-prison.html | title = Three Aruba suspects going to prison | accessdate = 2016-06-01 | date = 2005-06-15 | publisher = Fox News Channel | quote = Police Superintendent Jan van der Straaten told The Associated Press Croes was detained based on information from one of the other three detainees. | deadurl = no }}</ref>。2005年中期至2006年主持案件调查的[[警察总监|警察总监]]格罗尔德·多姆皮格（{{lang|en|Gerold Dompig}}）称，从芒廷布鲁克来的这些学生都是在疯狂地参加聚会，而且大量饮酒，每天都会有很多人在别人的房间过夜。[[假日酒店|假日酒店]]为此还向这些学生直言，不欢迎他们明年再来。“至于娜塔莉更是一天到晚喝个没完，有证人称她每天一大早就要喝鸡尾酒，而且喝得太多，有两天根本没去吃早餐。”<ref name="Vanity" />霍洛威的同学利兹·凯恩（{{lang|en|Liz Cain}}）和克莱尔·菲尔曼（{{lang|en|Claire Fierman}}）也承认同学们的确喝得太多<ref name="dompigalcohol">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306132055/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/natalee-holloway-new-clues/ | deadurl = no | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/natalee-holloway-new-clues/ | title = Natalee Holloway: New Clues | accessdate = 2007-04-28 | date = 2006-03-25 | publisher = [[CBS新闻|CBS News]] | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。

同学们最后一次看到娜塔莉是在5月30日（星期一）凌晨1点30分左右<ref name="FBI Holloway">{{cite web | title = Seeking information: Disappearance of Natalee Ann Holloway | publisher = [[联邦调查局|Federal Bureau of Investigation]] | url = http://www.fbi.gov/wanted/seekinfo/holloway.htm | accessdate = 2010-09-23 | archivedate = 2010-09-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100923233330/http://www.fbi.gov/wanted/seekinfo/holloway.htm | deadurl = yes }}</ref>，她正同17岁的荷兰优等生约兰·范德斯洛特（{{lang|en|Joran van der Sloot}}）一起离开阿鲁巴当地连锁酒吧暨夜总会卡洛斯和查理（{{lang|en|Carlos'n Charlie's}}）<ref name="Court TV 2005-06-10">{{cite web | archivedate = 2009-01-09 | title = Lawyer: Missing Alabama teen went to beach with men before she disappeared | accessdate = 2009-01-09 | date = 2005-06-10 | publisher = Court TV | url = http://www.courttv.com/news/2005/0610/aruba_ap.html | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090109175720/http://www.courttv.com/news/2005/0610/aruba_ap.html }}</ref>。范德斯洛特是阿鲁巴当地居民，正在[[阿鲁巴国际学校|阿鲁巴国际学校]]就读<ref name="MSNBC 2005-07-05">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308140059/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/8435397/ | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/8435397/ | title = Two brothers freed in Aruba | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | date = 2005-07-05 | publisher = MSNBC | agency = Associated Press }}</ref>，同行的还有他的两个朋友，来自[[苏里南|苏里南]]的迪帕克·卡尔珀（{{lang|en|Deepak Kalpoe}}，21岁）和萨蒂什·卡尔珀（{{lang|en|Satish Kalpoe}}，18岁），两人是亲兄弟<ref name="CNN 2005-06-25">{{cite news | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2005/LAW/06/26/aruba.missing/ | title = Two Aruba suspects ordered released | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | date = 2005-06-25 | publisher = CNN | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304025901/http://edition.cnn.com/2005/LAW/06/26/aruba.missing/ }}</ref>，四人一起坐进迪帕克的车<ref name="CNN 2006-05-31" /><ref name="CBS News 2006-02-17">{{cite news | title = Holloway Parents Sue Dutch Teen | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | date = 2006-02-17 | publisher = CBS News | agency = Associated Press | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306132027/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/holloway-parents-sue-dutch-teen/ | deadurl = no | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/holloway-parents-sue-dutch-teen/ | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。根据原订日程，霍洛威应该在5月30日深夜搭飞机返回美国，但她没有赶到机场登机<ref name="Court TV 2005-06-08" />，已经打包好的行装和护照都还在酒店房间里<ref name="CNN 2006-05-31" /><ref name="Vanity" />。阿鲁巴有关部门开始在岛上各地及近海水域搜索，但一无所获<ref name="CNN 2006-05-31" />。

== 调查 ==

=== 早期侦查 ===
2005年5月30日，尤格·特威蒂和贝丝·特威蒂夫妇在女儿错过返程班机后立即同朋友一起乘私人飞机抵达阿鲁巴<ref name="ABC News 2006-02-23" />。降落不到四小时后，夫妻二人已向阿鲁巴警方提供范德斯洛特的姓名和住址，称女儿就是和这个人一起离开夜总会<ref name="ABC News 2006-02-23" />。据贝丝所说，假日酒店夜班经理从录像带上认出范德斯洛特，然后告诉她他的全名<ref name="HansenSearch" />。夫妻俩和几位朋友同两名阿鲁巴警官一起前往范德斯洛特家中寻找娜塔莉，范德斯洛特起初声称不知道娜塔莉的名字<ref name="Vanity" />，但之后又称娜塔莉离开夜总会后想去看鲨鱼，所以他们开车前往阿尔希海滩（{{lang|en|Arashi Beach}}）的加利福尼亚灯塔（{{lang|en|California Lighthouse}}）区域，然后在凌晨2点左右把她送回酒店<ref name="3More">{{cite web | archivedate = 2009-01-09 | title = Three more arrested in Aruba case of missing teen | accessdate = 2009-01-09 | date = 2005-06-09 | publisher = CNN | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.courttv.com/news/2005/0609/holloway_cnn.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090109181441/http://www.courttv.com/news/2005/0609/holloway_cnn.html }}</ref>。范德斯洛特还称，霍洛威在下车时摔倒，但拒绝接受他的帮助<ref name="3More" />。他们驾车离开时还看到一名深色皮肤的男子走到她身边，这名男子身上穿着类似酒店保安制服的黑色衬衫<ref name="3More" />。范德斯洛特向警方做出上述供述时，迪帕克·卡尔珀就在一旁，他确认范德斯洛特的说法属实<ref name="Vanity" />。

[[File:CarlosnCharlies_Oranjestad,_Aruba.jpg|thumb]]的卡洛斯和查理夜总会，霍洛威的同学就是在这里最后一次看见她。]]

有关部门立即着手寻找霍洛威，参加搜索的还有来自阿鲁巴和美国的数百名志愿者。搜寻工作开始当天，阿鲁巴政府还让数以千计的公务员放假前去参加搜索。<ref name="LA Times 2007-06-04" />50名[[荷兰皇家海军陆战队|荷兰皇家海军陆战队员]]仔细搜索阿鲁巴岛海岸沿线<ref name="MSNBC 2005-06-06" />。岛上多家银行筹得2万美元资金，并为志愿搜索队提供其它多种形式的帮助和支持<ref name="demonstration" />。假日酒店主动向贝丝提供住宿，让她住进女儿之前住的同一间房<ref name="lighton">{{cite news | title = Holloway's mom a media star | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | date = 2005-07-05 | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/07/05/holloway-mom-media-star.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160307084620/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/07/05/holloway-mom-media-star.html | publisher = Fox News Channel | archivedate = 2016-03-07 }}</ref>。不过贝丝之后又离开假日酒店，住在附近[[温德姆酒店及度假村|温德姆酒店]]的总统套房<ref name="Vanity" />。

据报导，霍洛威失踪当晚没有出现在假日酒店大堂的[[闭路电视|监控录像]]中<ref name="NewDNat">{{cite news | first = Nancy | last = Grace | title = New Developments in the Natalee Holloway Case | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | date = 2006-04-19 | publisher = CNN | url = http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0604/19/ng.01.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304110533/http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0604/19/ng.01.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。不过，贝丝·特威蒂对这些摄像头当晚是否正常运作说法前后不一。她曾于2006年4月19日称假日酒店的监视摄像头在女儿失踪当晚没有正常工作<ref name="NewDNat" />，但在2007年出版的著作中又持完全相反的说法<ref name="MSNBC 2005-12-05">{{cite web | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/10348437/ | title = Rita Cosby Live & Direct | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | date = 2005-12-05 | publisher = MSNBC | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308140103/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/10348437/ | archivedate = 2016-03-08 }}</ref><ref name="BethBook">{{cite book | last = Holloway | first = Beth | author2 = Sunny Tillman | title = Loving Natalee : A Mother's Testament of Hope and Faith | url = https://archive.org/details/lovingnataleemot0000holl | year = 2007 | publisher = HarperOne | location = New York | isbn = 978-0-06-145227-7 | oclc = 154702068}}</ref>。从立案开始主持调查直至2005年退休时止的警察总监扬·范德斯特拉滕（{{lang|en|Jan van der Straten}}）对此称，霍洛威当晚肯定没有经酒店大堂返回房间<ref name="CNN 2005-06-02">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045946/http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0506/02/ng.01.html | deadurl = no | url = http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0506/02/ng.01.html | title = Nancy Grace | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | date = 2005-06-02 | publisher = CNN | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。

案件侦查过程中大量搜寻物证，但其中也几次受到假线索的干扰。例如办案人员曾在迪帕克·卡尔珀的车上取得疑似血样，但经过检验却认定这根本就不是血液。<ref name="Fox News 2005-06-13">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160310212618/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/06/13/three-suspects-in-holloway-case-change-stories.html | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/06/13/three-suspects-in-holloway-case-change-stories.html | title = Three Suspects in Holloway Case Change Stories | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | date = 2005-06-13 | publisher = Fox News Channel | archivedate = 2016-03-10 }}</ref>

美国执部机构从调查初期就开始大量参与案件调查工作。[[美国国务卿|美国国务卿]][[康多莉扎·赖斯|康多莉扎·赖斯]]向记者称，[[美国联邦政府|联邦政府]]经常就此同阿鲁巴当局接触。[[美国国务院|美国国务院]]另一位官员称，应阿鲁巴政府官员连续多次主动要求，美国正投入大量资源参与案件调查。<ref name="Fox News 2005-06-15">{{cite news | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306180448/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/06/15/too-little-too-late.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/06/15/too-little-too-late.html | title = Too little, too late? | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | date = 2005-06-15 | publisher = Fox News Channel }}</ref>

=== 初期拘捕的多名嫌疑人 ===
6月5日，阿鲁巴警方逮捕尼克·约翰（{{lang|en|Nick John}}）和亚伯拉罕·琼斯（{{lang|en|Abraham Jones}}）<ref name="CBS News 2005-06-09">{{cite news | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/aruban-pm-takes-to-air-waves/ | title = Aruban PM takes to airwaves | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | date = 2005-06-09 | publisher = CBS News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160309055332/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/aruban-pm-takes-to-air-waves/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-09 }}</ref>，怀疑两人绑架并杀害了娜塔莉<ref name="MSBNC 2005-06-09">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308140043/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/8079019/ | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/8079019/ | title = Suspects in teen's disappearance remain jailed | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | date = 2005-06-09 | publisher = MSNBC }}</ref>。两人都曾在假日酒店附近的阿勒格罗酒店（{{lang|en|Allegro Hotel}}）当[[保全|保安]]<ref name="CNN 2005-06-09" />，但该酒店在案发时已停业装修<ref name="Fox News 2005-06-04">{{cite news | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/06/04/three-probed-in-missing-teen-case.html | title = Three probed in missing teen case | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | date = 2005-06-04 | publisher = Fox News Channel | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306182111/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/06/04/three-probed-in-missing-teen-case.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。警方此后一直没有正式公布拘捕两人的原因，但据新闻报导，两人有可能是因范德斯洛特和卡尔珀的陈述被捕<ref name="Oglesby 2005-06-15">{{cite news | last = Oglesby | first = Christy | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2005/WORLD/americas/06/15/aruba.arrests/ | title = Was race a factor in Aruba arrests? | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | date = 2005-06-15 | publisher = CNN | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305003634/http://edition.cnn.com/2005/WORLD/americas/06/15/aruba.arrests/ }}</ref><ref name="Fox News 2005-06-26">{{cite news | title = Questions Surround Aruba Probe | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306182727/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/06/26/questions-surround-aruba-probe.html | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/06/26/questions-surround-aruba-probe.html | date = 2005-06-26 | publisher = Fox News Channel | agency = Associated Press | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。另据报道，被捕的两人经常在不同酒店游荡，勾搭女性，至少一人还曾同执法部门发生事端<ref name="CBS News 2005-06-10">{{cite news | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/kisses-tryst-in-aruba-case/ | title = Kisses, tryst in Aruba case | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160312105756/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/kisses-tryst-in-aruba-case/ | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | date = 2005-06-10 | publisher = CBS News | archivedate = 2016-03-12 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。6月13日，警方决定不提出起诉，将约翰和琼斯释放<ref name="CNN 2005-06-25" />。

[[File:Joran_van_der_Sloot_Aruba_mugshot.jpg|thumb]]

2005年6月9日，警方以绑架并谋杀霍洛威的罪名逮捕范德斯洛特和卡尔珀兄弟<ref name="MSNBC 2005-06-13">{{cite web | work = NBCNews.com | date = 2005-06-13 | title = Scarborough Country for June 10 | accessdate = 2016-06-02 | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/8205946/ns/msnbc-morning_joe/t/scarborough-country-june/ | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160316155435/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/8205946/ns/msnbc-morning_joe/t/scarborough-country-june/ | archivedate = 2016-03-16 }}</ref>。根据阿鲁巴法律，办案人员可以在刑事案件调查过程中逮捕有重大嫌疑的调查对象，但要继续羁押嫌疑人，警方必须提供更为充分和严密的证据以供审查<ref name="MSBNC 2005-06-09" /><ref name="AP 2005-07-06">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | date = 2005-07-06 | title = Mother of missing Ala. teen asks countries to deny freed brothers asylum | publisher = CourtTV | accessdate = 2009-01-09 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.courttv.com/news/2005/0706/arubamother_ap.html | archivedate = 2009-01-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20090109150128/http://www.courttv.com/news/2005/0706/arubamother_ap.html }}</ref>。据多姆皮格表示，三人从一开始就是侦破人员的重点调查对象<ref name="dompigalcohol" />。他还称，霍洛威失踪案发三天后，警方就开始监控三人，除人身监视和电话窃听外还在监控他们的电子邮件<ref name="dompigalcohol" />。但由于受到霍洛威家人的压力，警方不得不过早中止监控，逮捕三名嫌疑人<ref name="dompigalcohol" />。

案件调查期间，阿鲁巴司法部发言人大卫·克鲁兹（{{lang|en|David Cruz}}）于6月11日称娜塔莉·霍洛威已经死亡，当局知道尸体的下落<ref name="Fox News 2005-06-11">{{cite news | publisher = Fox News Channel | date = 2005-06-11 | title = Reports Conflict in Case of Missing Ala. Teen | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | archivedate = 2016-03-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160315011050/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/06/11/reports-conflict-in-case-missing-ala-teen.html | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/06/11/reports-conflict-in-case-missing-ala-teen.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>。但他之后又收回上述言论，称受到假情报的误导<ref name="Fox News 2005-06-11" />。多姆皮格当晚告知[[美联社|美联社]]，被捕的三人中已有一人供称他们把娜塔莉带到海滩后“发生了不好的事”，而且正带领警方赶赴现场<ref name="Fox News 2005-06-11" />。次日早上，检方发言人维维安·范德比赞（{{lang|en|Vivian van der Biezen}}）拒绝确认或否认多姆皮格的说法，称案件调查已经到了“非常关键、非常重要的时刻”<ref name="Fox News 2005-06-11" />。

6月17日（星期五），警方又逮捕一名嫌疑人，其身份经之后确认是[[唱片骑师|唱片骑师]]史蒂夫·格雷戈里·克罗伊斯（{{lang|en|Steve Gregory Croes}}）。范德斯特拉滕向媒体透露，警方是根据被捕三名嫌疑人中一人的供述逮捕克罗伊斯<ref name="FNCThree" />。6月22日，阿鲁巴警方又将约兰·范德斯洛特的父亲保卢斯·范德斯洛特（{{lang|en|Paulus van der Sloot}}）带到警局问话，并在当天将他逮捕。不过，保卢斯和克罗伊斯均于6月26日获释<ref name="CNN 2005-06-25" />。

在此期间，仍被警方拘留的三名嫌疑人都改变原有说辞<ref name="CNN 2005-06-25" />。三人都称范德斯洛特和霍洛威当晚是在[[万豪国际|万豪酒店]]的海滩附近下车，旁边还有幢渔民棚屋。范德斯洛特声称并没有伤害霍洛威，只是把她留在海滩上。<ref name="Fox News 2005-08-02">{{cite news | publisher = Fox News Channel | date = 2005-08-02 | title = Natalee suspect questioned by specialists | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | archivedate = 2016-03-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160313221628/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/08/02/natalee-suspect-questioned-by-specialists.html | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/08/02/natalee-suspect-questioned-by-specialists.html }}</ref>另据萨蒂什·卡尔珀的律师大卫·科克（{{lang|en|David Kock}}）所述，范德斯洛特之后打通萨蒂什的电话，说自己正走路回家，并在40分钟后发来短信<ref name="CNN 2005-06-25" />。

范德斯洛特受审期间还曾给出第三种说法，称卡尔珀兄弟把他送回家后再驾车同霍洛威离去<ref name="Vanity" />，但多姆皮格认为这一供述并不可信，称：

<blockquote>（范德斯洛特）最新的说法指向卡尔珀兄弟，这一定程度上只是他在指责别人，希望通过声称自己之前就已下车来凸显（卡尔珀）兄弟俩的嫌疑。但他的说法完全同事实不符，只是想让迪帕克也惹上一身臊。他们为此在法官面前争论不休，各人的说法也不吻合。这个姑娘（指霍洛威）是从阿拉巴马州来的，她可不会和两个黑人男孩一起留在车上。我们觉得第二种说法的可能性较大，他们是在万豪酒店附近下车。<ref name="Vanity" />
</blockquote>

7月4日（星期一），法官在对三名嫌疑人过堂聆讯后决定释放卡尔珀兄弟二人，但警方可以继续拘留范德斯洛特60天<ref name="BBC News 2005-06-04">{{cite news | publisher = BBC News | date = 2005-06-04 | title = Judge frees two Aruba suspects | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/4650727.stm | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305075040/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/4650727.stm | archivedate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>。

=== 继续搜寻，再度逮捕及释放嫌疑人 ===
[[File:NataleeHollowaySearch.jpg|thumb]]在加利福尼亚灯塔附近寻找霍洛威。]]
7月4日，[[荷兰皇家空军|荷兰皇家空军]]出动三架配有[[红外线|红外线]]传感器的[[F-16战隼战斗机|F-16战斗机]]协助搜寻，但起初仍然没有结果<ref name="LA Times 2007-06-04" /><ref name="AP 2007-11-22, F16" />。2006年3月，有报导称当局正将新近拍摄的照片（估计就是由{{lang|en|F}}-16战斗机拍摄）同卫星照片对比，希望能在地面找到微小的地势变化，这有可能就是霍洛威被埋的地方<ref name="BBC News 2006-01-17">{{cite news | publisher = BBC News | date = 2006-01-17 | title = Aruba 'close to solving' case | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160509115929/http://www.bbc.co.uk/caribbean/news/story/2006/01/060117_arubaholloway.shtml | url = http://www.bbc.co.uk/caribbean/news/story/2006/01/060117_arubaholloway.shtml | archivedate = 2016-05-09 }}</ref>。

2005年7月27至30日，当局在收到举报后把阿鲁巴网球俱乐部位于万豪酒店附近的一口小池塘部分抽乾，据称举报者是该俱乐部的园丁<ref name="CNN 2005-07-27">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | date = 2005-07-27 | title = Draining of Aruba pond begins | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2005/LAW/07/26/aruba.missing/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306210326/http://www.cnn.com/2005/LAW/07/26/aruba.missing/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。另据尤格·特威蒂所述，这位园丁自称于5月30日凌晨2点30分至3点看到约兰·范德斯洛特和卡尔珀兄弟乘车进入俱乐部，范德斯洛特在此期间还试图挡住脸，避免被他人认出<ref name="CBS News 2005-07-27">{{cite news | publisher = CBS News | date = 2005-07-27 | title = Pond Search Continues in Aruba | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306132031/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/pond-search-continues-in-aruba/ | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/pond-search-continues-in-aruba/ | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。曾担任[[检察官|检察官]]的司法[[时事评论员|时事评论员]]、电视记者兼节目主持人[[南希·格雷斯|南希·格雷斯]]（{{lang|en|Nancy Grace}}）称这位园丁的证词“给案件带来突破性进展”<ref name="CNN 2005-08-12">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304045004/http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0508/12/ng.01.html | deadurl = no | date = 2005-08-12 | title = Transcripts: Nancy Grace for August 12, 2005, CNNHN | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0508/12/ng.01.html }}</ref>。另外，还有人自称5月30日下午慢跑时看到多名男子在[[堆填|填埋场]]掩埋某个金发女子<ref name="MSNBC 2005-07-31">{{cite web | publisher = MSNBC | date = 2005-07-31 | title = Aruban police again search landfill | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306214711/http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0508/12/ng.01.html | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/8745217/ | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。警方本已在霍洛威失踪后搜索过这片填埋场<ref name="MSNBC 2005-07-31" />，但在接到上述线报后，这里又被搜索过三次，其中一次还是联邦调查局动用[[搜索及拯救犬|寻尸犬]]开展<ref name="CNN 2005-08-01">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | date = 2005-08-01 | title = Missing teen's mother leaves Aruba | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306204247/http://www.cnn.com/2005/LAW/07/31/aruba.missing/ | deadurl = no | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2005/LAW/07/31/aruba.missing/ }}</ref>，但每次都一无所获<ref name="Vanity" />。

2005年7月25日，霍洛威的家人把帮助娜塔莉平安返回的悬赏金从20万提高到100万美元，提供线索帮助找到遗体的悬赏金额也有10万美元<ref name="CNN 2005-07-26">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | date = 2005-07-26 | title = Aruba case reward rises to $1 million | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2005/LAW/07/25/aruba.missing/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306205552/http://www.cnn.com/2005/LAW/07/25/aruba.missing/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。霍洛威失踪后，她的家人马上就悬赏5万美元，希望她平安归来<ref name="reward" />。2005年8月，针对霍洛威遗体下落的悬赏金额又从10万提高到25万美元<ref name="FCN-20050809">{{cite news | last = Prengman | first = Peter | date = 2005-08-09 | title = Missing Teen Family raises reward | newspaper = Daily News | agency = Associated Press | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1696&dat=20050809&id=rwAbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=HEkEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6655,975360 | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | archive-date = 2019-03-05 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190305004232/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1696&dat=20050809&id=rwAbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=HEkEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6655,975360 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

联邦调查局宣布，阿鲁巴有关部门已提供文档、嫌犯审讯纪录及其他证据。由阿鲁巴警方和检察机关人员共同组成的代表团前往联邦调查局位于[[匡提科|匡提科]]的中心实验室，同美方侦察人员交流。<ref name="CNN 2005-07-26" />办案人员找到一截粘有金色头发的[[牛皮胶布|管道胶带]]，这截胶带之后还经过荷兰及匡提科的实验室检测<ref name="CNN 2005-07-18">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | date = 2005-07-18 | title = FBI, Aruban authorities to test hair in search for missing girl | url = http://www.cnn.com/2005/LAW/07/18/aruba.missing/ | accessdate = 2006-01-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20060127201919/http://www.cnn.com/2005/LAW/07/18/aruba.missing/ | archivedate = 2006-01-27 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。但是，联邦调查局之后宣布这并不是霍洛威的头发<ref name="CNN 2005-07-29">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | date = 2005-07-29 | title = DNA on duct tape not missing teen's | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306205638/http://www.cnn.com/2005/LAW/07/28/aruba.missing/ | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2005/LAW/07/28/aruba.missing/ | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

8月26日，卡尔珀兄弟二人再度被捕，一起被捕的还有一名新嫌疑人<ref name="divers" />。这名嫌疑人名叫弗雷迪·阿拉巴兹斯（{{lang|en|Freddy Arambatzis}}），是范德斯洛特的朋友，被捕时21岁，据他的律师所说，阿拉巴兹斯涉嫌的罪名是同未成年女性发生不当关系并拍摄照片，但即便情况属实，事情也发生在霍洛威失踪前。范德斯洛特的母亲安妮塔称，这不过是执法机关孤注一掷地想要逼迫嫌疑人招供，但他们“根本就没有什么好交待的。”<ref name="Fox News 2005-09-01">{{cite news | publisher = Fox News Channel | date = 2005-09-01 | title = Aruba suspects accused of taking sex photos of another girl | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | archivedate = 2016-03-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160314095255/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/09/01/aruba-suspects-accused-taking-sex-photos-another-girl.html | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/09/01/aruba-suspects-accused-taking-sex-photos-another-girl.html }}</ref>警方没有正式说明再次逮捕卡尔珀兄弟的原因，多姆皮格之后称此举是为了向两人施压，让他们招供，但显然无济于事<ref name="Vanity" />。

2005年9月3日，虽然检方希望能继续拘留嫌犯，但法官还是命令警方释放全部四名嫌疑人，但也要求四人不要离开所在地，继续配合警方工作<ref name="AMW 2008-02-15">{{cite web | publisher = America's Most Wanted | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130318053752/http://www.amw.com/missing_persons/case.cfm?id=32411 | date = 2008-02-15 | title = AMW missing data file for Natalee Holloway: All Suspects Released | accessdate = 2013-03-18 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.amw.com/missing_persons/case.cfm?id=32411 | archivedate = 2013-03-18 }}</ref>。9月14日，[[荷属安的列斯和阿鲁巴联合上诉法院|荷属安的列斯和阿鲁巴联合上诉法院]]下令取消针对所有嫌犯的行动限制<ref name="timeline1">{{cite news | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/elements/2005/06/08/in_depth_us/timeline700368_0_main.shtml | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20081104082325/http://www.cbsnews.com/elements/2005/06/08/in_depth_us/timeline700368_0_main.shtml | archivedate = 2008-11-04 | title = Natalee Holloway timeline | accessdate = 2008-11-04 | date = 2008-01-31 | publisher = CBS News }}</ref>。

约兰·范德斯洛特在获释后的几个月里多次接受采访，阐述他对案情的看法，这其中最引人关注的就是[[福克斯新闻频道|福克斯新闻频道]]的一次长时间采访，于2006年3月分三个晚上播出。范德斯洛特在采访中声称霍洛威失踪当晚想同他发生性关系，但他因身上没有[[避孕套|避孕套]]而拒绝。<ref name="ABC News 2006-02-22">{{cite web |publisher=ABC News |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305015055/http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/story?id=1648218 |date=2006-02-22 |deadurl=no |archivedate=2016-03-05 |title=Joran van der Sloot Talks About Night With Natalee Holloway |accessdate=2016-06-03 |url=http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/story?id=1648218 }}</ref>他还称，霍洛威当时希望大家都留在海滩上，但他第二天早上必须去学校，所以不能久留。萨蒂什·卡尔珀约在凌晨三点来接范德斯洛特，把霍洛威独自一人留在海滩上。<ref name="Fox News 2006-03-01">{{cite news | publisher = Fox News Channel | date = 2006-03-01 | title = Transcript: Joran van der Sloot Goes 'On the Record,' Part 1 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306181806/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/03/01/transcript-joran-van-der-sloot-goes-on-record-part-1.html | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | quote = Well, I mean I had—I had to go to school the next day. I was close to my exams to do my final exams and, you know, the bus was picking me up at 6:40 am | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/03/01/transcript-joran-van-der-sloot-goes-on-record-part-1.html }}</ref>。但是，萨蒂什的律师科克于2005年8月表示，他的当事人那时已经入睡，根本没有驾车前往海滩把范德斯洛特送回家<ref name="Fox News 2005-08-24">{{cite news | publisher = Fox News Channel | date = 2005-08-24 | title = Free and clear? (excerpt from ''On the Record'') | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/08/24/free-and-clear.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160310164421/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2005/08/24/free-and-clear.html | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | archivedate = 2016-03-10 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。范德斯洛特还在采访中称，虽然这是霍洛威的要求，但他还是对把这么个年轻女子独自留在海滩上感到惭愧，他一开始没有说实话主要是因为觉得霍洛威肯定很快就会出现<ref name="Fox News 2006-03-01" />。

2006年1月，联邦调查局和阿鲁巴当局在美国走访霍洛威的多名同学，其中有些之前就已接受询问<ref name="Fox News 2006-01-27">{{cite news | publisher = Fox News Channel | date = 2006-01-27 | title = On the Record—Hunting for Answers (Transcript) | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/01/27/transcript-hunting-for-answers.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306181804/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/01/27/transcript-hunting-for-answers.html | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。2006年1月17日，阿鲁巴警方在该岛西北沿海地区的沙丘和万豪酒店海滩附近寻找霍洛威的尸体<ref name="CBS News 2006-03-29">{{cite news | publisher = CBS News | date = 2006-03-29 | title = Sources: Search resuming for Natalee | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306132017/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/sources-search-resuming-for-natalee/ | deadurl = no | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/sources-search-resuming-for-natalee/ }}</ref>。此外，当局还在2006年3月和4月再度开展搜索，但仍然没有取得进展<ref name="dompigalcohol" />。

多姆皮格曾在退出案件调查前不久接受[[CBS_(电视网)|CBS电视网]]特派记者特洛伊·罗伯茨（{{lang|en|Troy Roberts}}）采访，内容于2006年3月25日播映。多姆皮格在采访中称，霍洛威很可能不是遭他人谋杀，而是饮酒過量或药物中毒致死，然后有人把她的尸体藏了起来。他还称，阿鲁巴为案件调查已经花费约300万美元，其中约40%是警方工作开销。<ref name="dompigalcohol" />另据多姆皮格所述，有证据表明霍洛威拥有一些药品，只是不足以证明她肯定在服用<ref name="Alcohol" /><ref name="Fox News 2006-03-24">{{cite news | publisher = Fox News Channel | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160309202120/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/03/24/aruba-police-probe-drug-alcohol-role-in-holloway-case.html | date = 2006-03-24 | title = Aruba Police Probe Drug, Alcohol Role in Holloway Case | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/03/24/aruba-police-probe-drug-alcohol-role-in-holloway-case.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-09 }}</ref>。霍洛威的家人则称她根本没有服用药品<ref name="MSNBC 2006-03-24">{{cite web | publisher = MSNBC | date = 2006-03-24 | title = Scarborough Country for March 23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308140052/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/11993333 | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/11993333 | accessdate = 2016-06-03 }}</ref>。

2006年4月11日，戴夫·霍洛威出版著作《[[阿魯巴：娜塔莉·霍洛威不為人知的悲劇故事和天堂裡的腐敗|阿魯巴：娜塔莉·霍洛威不為人知的悲劇故事和天堂裡的腐敗]]》（{{lang|en|''Aruba: The Tragic Untold Story of Natalee Holloway and Corruption in Paradise''}}），在书中回顾寻找女儿的经过。该书由同他和{{lang|en|R}}·斯蒂芬妮·古德（{{lang|en|R. Stephanie Good}}）和拉里·加里森（{{lang|en|Larry Garrison}}）共同创作。<ref name="DHolloway 2006, ch. Everybody's Child / Aruba" /><ref name="Fox News 2006-04-11">{{cite news | publisher = Fox News Channel | date = 2006-04-11 | title = Transcript: Corruption in paradise? | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/04/11/transcript-corruption-in-paradise.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306204312/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/04/11/transcript-corruption-in-paradise.html | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

=== 2006年：逮捕新嫌疑人，荷兰接手案件调查 ===
2006年4月15日，杰弗里·范·克隆沃伊特（{{lang|en|Geoffrey von Cromvoirt}}）因涉嫌[[非法毒品贸易|交易违禁麻醉品]]被阿鲁巴警方逮捕，检察官还称他有可能同霍洛威失踪案有关<ref name="ABC News 2006-04-17">{{cite web | publisher = ABC News | date = 2006-04-17 | title = Lawyer: Joran doesn't know man arrested in Holloway case | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205655/http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/story?id=1849859 | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | url = http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/story?id=1849859 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。克隆沃伊特首次上庭聆讯后，法官把警方拘留他的时间延长八天，他之后在这个月25日获释<ref name="Cromvoirt">{{cite news | title = Prosecutors: Holloway suspect van (sic) Cromvoirt freed | date = 2006-04-24 | publisher = CNN | url = http://www.cnn.com/2006/LAW/04/24/holloway/?eref=yahoo | accessdate = 2008-02-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080223235245/http://www.cnn.com/2006/LAW/04/24/holloway/?eref=yahoo | archivedate = 2008-02-23 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。此外，警方还于2006年4月22日逮捕某个姓名首字母缩写为“{{lang|en|A.B.}}”的嫌疑人，但当天就将他释放<ref name="Cromvoirt" />。

2006年5月17日，阿鲁巴前政客之子圭多·韦弗（{{lang|en|Guido Wever}}）在荷兰因涉嫌协助他人绑架、殴打并杀害霍洛威被捕<ref name="CNN 2006-05-22">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | date = 2006-05-22 | title = Suspect in Holloway case to be released | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2006/LAW/05/22/holloway/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305100241/http://edition.cnn.com/2006/LAW/05/22/holloway/ | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，然后在[[乌得勒支|乌得勒支]]接受为期六天的审问。阿鲁巴检方起初打算将韦弗引渡回岛，但检察官之后同韦弗的律师达成交易并将他释放。<ref name="Wever">{{cite news | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306182117/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/05/23/lawyer-natalee-holloway-suspect-is-gay.html | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2006/05/23/lawyer-natalee-holloway-suspect-is-gay.html | title = Lawyer: Natalee Holloway suspect "is gay" | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | date = 2006-03-23 | publisher = Fox News Channel }}</ref>

应阿鲁巴当局请求，荷兰于2006年9月开始接手案件侦破工作。从[[鹿特丹|鹿特丹]]获得大量案件纪录后，[[荷兰国家警察|荷兰国家警察]]工作组于同月开始着手调查。2007年4月16日，阿鲁巴和荷兰刑侦人员组成的联合调查组开始在岛上展开侦查。<ref name="KLPD">{{cite web | url = http://www.kparuba.com/newspages/persberichtNH28apr07.html | title = Gecombineerd rechercheteam onderzoekt vermissing Natalee Holloway | author = Korps landelijke politiediensten | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140714221333/http://www.kparuba.com/newspages/persberichtNH28apr07.html | archivedate = 2014-07-14 | accessdate = 2014-07-14 | date = 2007-04-28 }}</ref>

=== 嫌犯出书，继续搜寻和侦察 ===
2007年4月，约兰·范德斯洛特和记者威兹达纳·伍科耶维奇（{{lang|en|Zvezdana Vukojevic}}）共同创作的《[[娜塔莉·霍洛威案_(书)|娜塔莉·霍洛威案]]》（{{lang|en|''De zaak Natalee Holloway''}}）在荷兰出版<ref name="Van der Sloot 2007">{{cite book | last1 = Van der Sloot | first1 = Joran | author2 = Zvezdana Vukojevic | title = De zaak Natalee Holloway: mijn eigen verhaal over haar verdwijning op Aruba | year = 2007 | publisher = Sijthoff | location = Amsterdam | isbn = 978-90-218-0014-1 | oclc = 150235828}}</ref>。范德斯洛特在书中详述他对霍洛威失踪当晚的回忆和看法，以及案发后媒体的狂热炒作。他在书中承认一开始没有说实话并道歉，但坚称自己是清白的。<ref name="ABC/Brouwer 2007-11-28">{{cite news | publisher = ABC News | last = Brouwer | first = Christine | date = 2007-11-28 | title = Van der Sloot's Book gives his version of the night Natalee vanished | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304062328/http://abcnews.go.com/TheLaw/story?id=3925483 | deadurl = no | url = http://abcnews.go.com/TheLaw/Story?id=3925483 }}</ref>

2007年4月27日，约20名侦察人员在范德斯洛特一家位于阿鲁巴的宅邸开始新一轮搜查<ref name="AP/Wever 2007-04-27">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | last = Wever | first = Margaret | date = 2007-04-27 | title = Holloway probe continues in Aruba | publisher = ABC News}}</ref><ref name="CNN 2007-04-30">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306204809/http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0704/30/ng.01.html | deadurl = no | url = http://transcripts.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0704/30/ng.01.html | title = Investigators Search Natalee Holloway Disappearance Suspect's House | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | date = 2007-04-30 | publisher = CNN's Nancy Grace (Transcript) | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。荷兰的调查人员搜查了庭院及周边地区，使用铁锹和细金属棒检查泥土<ref name="AP/Wever 2007-04-27" />。检方发言人范德比赞称，案件调查工作其实一直都在继续，荷兰当局正全面检视案情，寻找新的突破口<ref name="AP/Wever 2007-04-27" />。检察机关还发表声明，称工作组是根据之前找到的线索决定开展更加彻底的搜查<ref name="AP/Wever 2007-04-27" />。调查人员称线索同范德斯洛特出的书有关<ref name="KLPD" />，但没有说明具体事项<ref name="AP/Wever 2007-04-27" />。保卢斯·范德斯洛特称这次搜查“没有（找到）任何可疑迹象”，侦察人员最后只拿走他和夫人的日记，以及他使用的电脑，之后又把电脑送了回来<ref name="CBS News 2007-05-01">{{cite news | publisher = CBS News | date = 2007-05-01 | title = New Natalee Holloway Search Pleases Family | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/new-natalee-holloway-search-pleases-family/ | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304033428/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/new-natalee-holloway-search-pleases-family/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

据《阿鲁巴日报》总编[[乔西·曼苏尔|乔西·曼苏尔]]（{{lang|en|Jossy Mansur}}）表示，卡尔珀兄弟和约兰·范德斯洛特在之前受审期间曾互通电话和电子邮件，侦察人员是据此跟进调查。曼苏尔还称，有人看到侦察人员在搜查时检查笔记本电脑。<ref name="NBC News May 2007">{{cite news | publisher = NBC News | date = 2007-05 | title = Investigators Search Kalpoe Brothers Home}}</ref>

2007年5月12日，卡尔珀一家的宅邸也受到搜查<ref name="KBrosNBC">{{cite web | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308133636/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/18630994/ | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/18630994/ | title = Investigators search home in Holloway case | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | date = 2007-03-12 | publisher = MSNBC }}</ref>。卡尔珀兄弟二人起初反对警察和荷兰办案人员进入，因此被拘留约一小时，直到这些人离开后获释<ref name="KBrosNBC" /><ref name="KBrosFOX">{{cite news | title = Kalpoe Brothers Home Inspected in Natalee Holloway Case | date = 2007-05 | publisher = FOX6WBRC}}</ref>。据科克所言，兄弟二人反对此次搜查主要是因为对方没有提供正当理由。范德比赞发布的声明中没有说明办案人员是在找什么，但他们没有从卡尔珀家中取走任何物品。<ref name="KBrosNBC" /><ref name="KBrosFOX" />阿鲁巴检方随后发表声明，称此次搜查旨在了解这起罪行有可能是在什么地方发生，又是在什么样的情况下发生<ref name="Antilliaans Dagblad 2007-05-15">{{cite news | publisher = Antilliaans Dagblad | date = 2007-05-15 | title = Onderzoek bij de broers Kalpoe | quote = een beter beeld krijgen van de plaats waar, of de omstandigheden waaronder, een delict zou zijn begaan, of waar sporen van betrokkenheid bij een delict kunnen worden vastgesteld}}</ref><ref name="RNW 2007-05-14">{{cite web | publisher = Radio Nederland Wereldomroep | date = 2007-05-14 | title = Huiszoekingen in zaak Holloway | accessdate = 2016-06-03 | url = http://archief.wereldomroep.nl/caribiana/article/huiszoekingen-zaak-holloway | archivedate = 2016-06-03 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160603164249/http://archief.wereldomroep.nl/caribiana/article/huiszoekingen-zaak-holloway | df =  }}</ref>。

=== 2007年：再次逮捕和释放嫌疑人 ===
2007年11月21日，阿鲁巴侦破人员声称发现新证据并再次逮捕卡尔珀兄弟和约兰·范德斯洛特，怀疑他们涉嫌“[[误杀|误杀]]或导致霍洛威重伤致死”。卡尔珀兄弟在阿鲁巴被拘，范德斯洛特起初被荷兰当局关押在荷兰本土，之后又转至阿鲁巴单独拘禁。<ref name="AP 2007-11-22, 3 re-arrested" />

2007年11月，戴夫·霍洛威宣布为女儿展开新一轮搜索行动，搜寻范围超过之前已经搜索过的海岛周边100米深海域<ref name="AP/Wever 2007-11-22, search">{{cite news |agency=Associated Press |last=Wever |first=Margaret |date=2007-11-22 |title=Missing Teen's Father to Search for Body |newspaper=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] |archiveurl=https://archive.today/20130205204349/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/11/22/AR2007112200288.html |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/11/22/AR2007112200288.html |accessdate=2016-06-04 |archivedate=2013-02-05 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。参与此次搜索的还有“持久号”（{{lang|en|Persistence}}）船只，但由于缺乏进展，搜索工作于2008年2月中止<ref name="sowhatelseisnew">{{cite web | last = Cisneros | first = Cynthia | url = http://abc13.com/archive/5988951/ | title = Holloway searchers need help | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160425180242/http://abc13.com/archive/5988951/ | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | archivedate = 2016-04-25 | date = 2008-02-28 | publisher = ABC KRTK | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

2007年11月30日，法官拒绝检方延长拘留时间的要求，下令释放卡尔珀兄弟<ref name="APKrelease">{{cite news | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/22044692/ | title = 2 suspects to be freed in Holloway case | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | date = 2007-11-30 | publisher = MSNBC | agency = Associated Press | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308134334/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/22044692/ }}</ref><ref name="NovRelease">{{cite episode | title = 2007-11-30 | series = Studio B | publisher = Fox News Channel  | airdate = 2007-11-30 | credits = Greta Van Susteren and Neil Cavuto}}</ref>，两人于次日获释<ref name="CNN 2007-12-01">{{cite news | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2007/WORLD/americas/12/01/aruba.holloway/ | title = Brothers in Holloway case walk away from jails – again | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | date = 2007-12-01 | publisher = CNN | archivedate = 2016-04-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160427155844/http://edition.cnn.com/2007/WORLD/americas/12/01/aruba.holloway/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。检方对此提出上诉，法院于同年12月5日驳回上诉，称案件调查虽然已经花费大量时间和花销，但检方提供的证据还不足以直接证明霍洛威死于暴力罪行<ref name="USA Today 2007-12-05">{{cite news | publisher = Gannett | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160428111121/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/world/2007-12-05-aruba-missing-teen_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/world/2007-12-05-aruba-missing-teen_N.htm | title = Appeal denied in release of Holloway suspects | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | date = 2007-12-05 | agency = Associated Press | work = USA Today | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-04-28 }}</ref>。2007年12月7日，由于缺乏证据证明霍洛威死于暴力，也没有足够证据说明犯罪嫌疑，范德斯洛特再度获释，检方这次表示不会上诉<ref name="CNN 2007-12-07">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160427114723/http://edition.cnn.com/2007/WORLD/americas/12/07/aruba/ | deadurl = no | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2007/WORLD/americas/12/07/aruba/ | title = Van der Sloot ordered released from Aruba jail | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | date = 2007-12-07 | publisher = CNN | archivedate = 2016-04-27 }}</ref>。

2007年12月18日，检察官汉斯·摩斯（{{lang|en|Hans Mos}}）正式宣布结案，由于缺少证据，当局不会起诉任何嫌疑人<ref name="Newsweek 2008-02-08">{{cite web | url = http://www.newsweek.com/cracking-holloway-case-93881 | title = Cracking the Holloway Case? | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | date = 2008-02-08 | work = Newsweek | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090319/http://www.newsweek.com/cracking-holloway-case-93881 | quote = Last December the case was officially closed for lack of evidence. | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref><ref name="People 2007-12-18">{{cite web |url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20166961,00.html?xid=rss-fullcontentcnn |title=Natalee Holloway Case Closed for Lack of Evidence |accessdate=2016-06-04 |date=2007-12-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307225857/http://www.people.com/people/article/0%2C%2C20166961%2C00.html?xid=rss-fullcontentcnn |work=[[人物_(杂志)|People]] |archivedate=2016-03-07 |publisher=Time }}</ref>。检方还表示，虽然约兰·范德斯洛特和卡尔珀兄弟不再是法律意义上的犯罪嫌疑人，但当局还是会继续对他们保持关注，还称其中一人曾在聊天室发信息说霍洛威已经死亡。检方上述说法引起迪帕克·卡尔珀律师的强烈质疑，称检方在把[[帕皮阿门托语|帕皮阿门托语]]翻译成荷兰语时误解原意，原话的意思是有某位教师溺毙，同霍洛威无关。<ref name="KBrosUSA">{{cite news | url = http://www.usatoday.com/news/topstories/2007-12-21-3066205443_x.htm | title = Defense Response to Aruban Prosecutors | accessdate = 2008-03-31 | date = 2007-12-21 | work = USA Today | agency = Associated Press | first = Margaret | last = Wever | archive-date = 2009-02-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090227085545/http://www.usatoday.com/news/topstories/2007-12-21-3066205443_x.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref>律师罗纳德·维克斯（{{lang|en|Ronald Wix}}）也称，除非摩斯能在某个男孩的浴室找到尸体，否则绝对不可能再来实施拘捕<ref name="ceeya">{{cite news | archivedate = 2012-10-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121001060402/http://www.citytv.com/toronto/citynews/news/local/article/19221--aruban-authorities-reveal-proof-in-case-of-missing-teen | title = Aruban Authorities Reveal 'Proof' In Case of Missing Teen | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2007-12-23 | date = 2007-12-20 | agency = Associated Press | url = http://www.citytv.com/toronto/citynews/news/local/article/19221--aruban-authorities-reveal-proof-in-case-of-missing-teen }}</ref>。

=== 隐秘摄像头，声明及多种说法 ===
2008年1月31日，荷兰罪案记者[[彼得·R·德弗里斯|彼得·R·德弗里斯]]（{{lang|en|Peter R. de Vries}}）自称已破解霍洛威失踪案，并且会在2月3日荷兰电视台的特别节目中揭秘<ref name="confession">{{cite web | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303213320/http://abcnews.go.com/TheLaw/Story?id=4230840 | deadurl = no | url = http://abcnews.go.com/TheLaw/Story?id=4230840 | title = Reporter Claims to Crack Natalee Holloway Case | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | date = 2008-01-31 | publisher = ABC News }}</ref>。贝丝·特威蒂的律师约翰·凯利（{{lang|en|John Q. Kelly}}）在接受[[ABC新闻|ABC新闻]]采访时称，他觉得德弗里斯所能提供的证据不大可能对案情产生重大影响，并且很快就会被揭穿<ref name="confession" />。

2月1日，荷兰媒体报导称约兰·范德斯洛特已就娜塔莉·霍洛威失踪案招供。范德斯洛特于当天回应称，他同霍洛威失踪一事无关，只是对别人说了对方想听到的话。<ref name="denial">{{cite news | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306132014/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/holloway-suspect-confesses-recants/ | deadurl = no | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/holloway-suspect-confesses-recants/ | title = Holloway Suspect Confesses, Recants | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | date = 2008-02-01 | publisher = CBS News }}</ref>阿鲁巴检察机关也在当天宣布恢复案件调查<ref name="ABC News 2008-02-03" />。

德弗里斯所说的特别节目于2008年2月3日播出，其中包括荷兰商人帕特里克·范德伊姆（{{lang|en|Patrick van der Eem}}）车上隐秘摄像头和话筒录下的内容节选。范德伊姆有犯罪前科，他是在获得范德斯洛特的信任后录下这些内容。<ref name="stoner">{{cite web |url=http://abcnews.go.com/TheLaw/story?id=4263979 |title=Investigators grill Joran van der Sloot |author=Chris Francescani |author2=Christine Brouwer |accessdate=2016-06-04 |date=2008-02-08 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150601214626/http://abcnews.go.com/TheLaw/story?id=4263979 |publisher=ABC News |archivedate=2015-06-01 |deadurl=no }}</ref>视频中可以看到范德斯洛特吸食[[大麻_(药用)|大麻]]<ref name="DutchNews 2008-02-03">{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160604040209/http://www.dutchnews.nl/news/archives/2008/02/natalee_will_never_be_found_sa/ | url = http://www.dutchnews.nl/news/archives/2008/02/natalee_will_never_be_found_sa/ | title = Natalee will never be found, says Joran | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | date = 2008-02-03 | publisher = DutchNews | archivedate = 2016-06-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，还称霍洛威开始抽搐颤抖、并且对外界刺激没有反应时他就在一旁。范德斯洛特在视频中称，他当时试图帮霍洛威恢复知觉，但徒劳无功。他接下来打电话给朋友，后者帮他处理掉尸体，叫他回家。<ref name="denial1">{{cite news | title = Hidden camera shows Dutch student saying Natalee Holloway died on Aruba beach | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | date = 2008-02-04 | publisher = Fox News Channel | archivedate = 2016-03-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160316094302/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2008/02/04/hidden-camera-footage-shows-holloway-suspect-confess-to-dumping-body-at-sea.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2008/02/04/hidden-camera-footage-shows-holloway-suspect-confess-to-dumping-body-at-sea.html }}</ref>节目中还称范德斯洛特的这位朋友名叫道瑞（{{lang|en|Daury}}），但他否认范德斯洛特的说法，称自己当时身在位于鹿特丹的学校<ref name="daury">{{cite web | url = http://abcnews.go.com/TheLaw/2020/story?id=4239135 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304083621/http://abcnews.go.com/TheLaw/2020/story?id=4239135 | title = Mystery man in Holloway case comes forward | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | date = 2008-02-05 | publisher = ABC News | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。

阿鲁巴检方以这卷录像为依据，向法官申请针对范德斯洛特的逮捕令，但法官没有同意<ref name="DutchNews 2008-01-04">{{cite web | url = http://www.dutchnews.nl/news/archives/2008/02/no_warrant_for_van_der_sloots/ | title = No warrant for Van Der Sloot's arrest: judge | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | date = 2008-01-04 | publisher = DutchNews | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160529072650/http://www.dutchnews.nl/news/archives/2008/02/no_warrant_for_van_der_sloots | archivedate = 2016-05-29 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。检察官提起上诉，但又于2008年2月14日遭驳回<ref name="RNW 2008-02-15">{{cite news | title = Court ignores confession in Holloway case | accessdate = 2010-09-13 | date = 2008-02-15 | url = http://static.rnw.nl/migratie/www.radionetherlands.nl/currentaffairs/080215-holloway-confession-redirected | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100913234145/http://static.rnw.nl/migratie/www.radionetherlands.nl/currentaffairs/080215-holloway-confession-redirected | publisher = Radio Netherlands | archivedate = 2010-09-13 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。上诉法院认为，录像带中的说法同案件已有证据不符，同时也不足以扣押范德斯洛特<ref name="ruling">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306183436/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2008/02/15/court-blocks-dutch-student-arrest-in-holloway-disappearance.html | title = Court blocks Dutch student's arrest in Holloway's disappearance | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2008-02-15 | date = 2008-02-15 | publisher = Fox News Channel | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2008/02/15/court-blocks-dutch-student-arrest-in-holloway-disappearance.html }}</ref>。

2008年2月8日，范德斯洛特在荷兰同阿鲁巴刑侦人员见面。范德斯洛特称自己当时吸了大麻，视频中的供认作不得准，他还坚称自己当晚是把霍洛威留在海滩上自行离开。<ref name="stoner" />

2008年3月，多份新闻报导表明局势已向不利于范德伊姆的方向转变，他在接受阿鲁巴电视台采访后也在不知情的情况下被录音。范德伊姆当时误以为摄影机已经关掉，于是向镜头透露自己已是范德斯洛特多年的好友，但他此前在德弗里斯的节目中自称是2007年才结识范德斯洛特。范德伊姆还表示，他本期望通过霍洛威失踪案成为百万富翁，也知道当时是谁处理掉霍洛威的遗体，还称范德斯洛特当时不得不找他借了2000[[欧元|欧元]]支付此人的封口费。另据[[荷兰新闻社|荷兰新闻社]]消息，此时已签下出书合同的范德伊姆得知上述内容被录制下来后“怒不可遏”，并一度威胁采访记者，后者为此还曾寻求法律意见。<ref name="DutchNews 2008-03-07">{{cite news | date = 2008-03-07 | publisher = DutchNews | url = http://www.dutchnews.nl/news/archives/2008/03/friend_knows_who_dumped_natale | archivedate = 2015-11-01 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151101160938/http://www.dutchnews.nl/news/archives/2008/03/friend_knows_who_dumped_natale | title = 'Friend' knows who dumped Natalee | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

2008年6月25日，范德伊姆同{{lang|en|E}}·{{lang|en|E}}·拜尔斯（{{lang|en|E.E. Byars}}）合著的《落水》一书出版（荷兰语）<ref name="nl dictionary">{{cite book | last1 = Visser | first1 = G. J. | last2 = de Knegt | first2 = A. F. M. | last3 = de Knegt-Bos | first3 = C. | year = 1996 | title = Prism Nederlands-Engels | url = https://archive.org/details/nederlandsengels0000viss | publisher = Prisma-Boeken | location = Utrecht | isbn = 978-90-274-5148-4 | page = [https://archive.org/details/nederlandsengels0000viss/page/260 260]}}</ref><ref name="moreboo">{{cite news | title = Van der Eem snoof bij Joran in auto | publisher = RTL Nieuws | date = 2008-06}}</ref>。2008年12月13日，艾德伊姆因涉嫌用撬棍殴打女友，并在逃离警方追捕时犯下危险驾驶罪在荷兰被捕<ref name="AD Van der Eem">{{cite web | accessdate = 2016-06-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303210906/http://www.ad.nl/ad/nl/1012/Nederland/article/detail/2118000/2008/12/18/Van-der-Eem-in-cel-voor-mishandeling-vriendin.dhtml?redirected | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | work = Algemeen Dagblad | url = http://www.ad.nl/ad/nl/1012/Nederland/article/detail/2118000/2008/12/18/Van-der-Eem-in-cel-voor-mishandeling-vriendin.dhtml?redirected | title = Van der Eem in cel voor mishandeling vriendin | deadurl = no | date = 2008-12-18 }}</ref>。

荷兰司法心理学家威廉·阿尔伯特·瓦赫纳尔（{{lang|en|Willem Albert Wagenaar}}）曾在某次研讨会上探讨德弗里斯的电视节目，称视频中范德斯洛特的说法还不足以认定成供述。瓦赫纳尔对德弗里斯播映这段视频持否定态度，称这会导致检方更难将嫌疑人定罪，如果德弗里斯在没有播出的情况下把视频素材直接交给有关部门，检方就会在质询范德斯洛特时拥有足够的主动权。瓦赫纳尔还指出，现在检方面临的问题不仅仅是破案，他们甚至无法确定这到底是不是犯罪事件。参加此次研讨会的克里斯基·布兰茨（{{lang|en|Crisje Brants}}）教授同样不认同德弗里斯的做法。<ref name="RNW 2008-02-11">{{cite web | title = Holloway confession on TV: Trial by psychology | accessdate = 2010-09-13 | date = 2008-02-11 | publisher = Radio Netherlands Worldwide | archivedate = 2010-09-13 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100913234139/http://static.rnw.nl/migratie/www.radionetherlands.nl/currentaffairs/080211-holloway-legal-sloot-redirected | url = http://static.rnw.nl/migratie/www.radionetherlands.nl/currentaffairs/080211-holloway-legal-sloot-redirected }}</ref>

2008年11月24日，福克斯新闻频道播出范德斯洛特的采访视频，后者自称已将霍洛威卖为[[性奴隶|性奴隶]]，对方还付款要求他保密。范德斯洛特声称，他的父亲还收买了两个得知霍洛威已被卖往[[委内瑞拉|委内瑞拉]]的警官。但是，范德斯洛特之后又收回上述说法。<ref name="Fox News 2008-11-24" />福克斯新闻频道的节目中还播出一段范德斯洛特提供的音频，据称是他和父亲的电话录音，其内容表明保卢斯知道儿子参与贩卖人口。但据摩斯所说，录音中另一个人的录音不是保卢斯·范德斯洛特，荷兰《[[电讯报|电讯报]]》也在报导中称，几乎可以肯定这不过是约兰自己刻意压低音调说话。<ref name="Telegraaf">{{cite web | url = http://www.telegraaf.nl/binnenland/article20761638.ece | title = Joran neemt Fox News in de maling | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | date = 2008-11-27 | work = De Telegraaf | archivedate = 2016-01-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160112035324/http://www.telegraaf.nl/binnenland/article20761638.ece }}</ref>2010年2月10日，保卢斯·范德斯洛特因心脏病发去世<ref name="RNW 2010-02-11">{{cite web | publisher = Radio Netherlands Worldwide | date = 2010-02-11 | title = Death of suspect's father complicates Natalee Holloway case | accessdate = 2012-04-05 | url = http://www.rnw.nl/english/article/death-suspects-father-complicates-natalee-holloway-case | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120405191216/http://www.rnw.nl/english/article/death-suspects-father-complicates-natalee-holloway-case | archivedate = 2012-04-05 }}</ref>。

2009年3月20日，戴夫·霍洛威带着搜救犬再度飞抵阿鲁巴，搜索该岛北部的一座小型[[水库|水库]]，有证人此前声称他女儿的遗骨可能藏在这里。阿鲁巴当局表示案件并没有新线索，但还是批准戴夫在水库搜寻。<ref name="MSNBC 2009-03-20">{{cite web | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/29798259/ | title = Holloway's father sends search dog to Aruba | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | date = 2009-03-20 | publisher = MSNBC | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308140036/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/29798259/ }}</ref>

2010年2月23日，有报导称约兰·范德斯洛特在接受采访时表示，他把霍洛威的尸体放在阿鲁巴某个[[河流湿地|沼泽]]内。但是，新任首席检察官彼得·布兰肯（{{lang|en|Peter Blanken}}）认为范德斯洛特所说明的地点、时间和人名根本不合情理，当局已经调查过，认定他就是在胡扯。<ref name="MSNBC 2010-02-23">{{cite web | title = Natalee Holloway confession called "fantasy" | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/35533792/ns/world_news-americas/t/natalee-holloway-confession-branded-fantasy/ | accessdate = 2010-02-23 | date = 2010-02-23 | publisher = MSNBC | archivedate = 2016-03-11 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160311135912/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/35533792/ns/world_news-americas/t/natalee-holloway-confession-branded-fantasy/ }}</ref>

2010年3月，阿鲁巴当局在接到一对美国夫妇的报告后开展水下搜索<ref name="National Ledger 2010-03-27">{{cite web | url = http://www.nationalledger.com/ledgerdc/article_272631046.shtml | title = Aruban Divers and Natalee Holloway Remains — What Was Found? | work = National Ledger | date = 2010-03-27 | accessdate = 2010-03-31 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100330072920/http://www.nationalledger.com/ledgerdc/article_272631046.shtml | archivedate = 2010-03-30 }}</ref>。据这对夫妇所说，他们在潜水时拍到某个看起来像人类骨骼遗骸的东西，可能是霍洛威的遗骨，阿鲁巴当局虽出动多名潜水员查探，但还是没有找到仍然遗骨<ref name="CNN 2010-03-24">{{cite news | title = Authorities call off underwater search for Natalee Holloway's remains | publisher = CNN | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/03/24/aruba.photo.remains/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131130042114/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/03/24/aruba.photo.remains/ | deadurl = no | date = 2010-03-24 | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | archivedate = 2013-11-30 }}</ref>。

=== 范德斯洛特向霍洛威的家人勒索金钱 ===
2010年3月29日，范德斯洛特同贝丝·特威蒂的律师凯利取得联系，声称愿意告知霍洛威的死因和遗体所在，但要求对方支付25万美元，并预付2万5000美元<ref name="CNN-interpol-extortion">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304034658/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/06/08/us.van.der.sloot.alabama/ | deadurl = no | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/06/08/us.van.der.sloot.alabama/ | title = Interpol: Van der Sloot tried to extort Holloway's mother | date = 2010-06-08 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | accessdate = 2016-06-05 }}</ref>。凯利将情况告知联邦调查局，该机构决定安排交易<ref name="Fox-20100611-holloway">{{cite news | publisher = Fox News Channel | title = Van Der Sloot Talking About Holloway to Peru Authorities: Is He Lying Again? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305140725/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2010/06/11/van-der-sloot-talking-about-holloway-to-peru-authorities-is-lying-again.html | date = 2010-06-11 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2010/06/11/van-der-sloot-talking-about-holloway-to-peru-authorities-is-lying-again.html | accessdate = 2016-06-05 }}</ref><ref name="ET-20100609-fbi">{{cite news | publisher = ETonline | title = FBI Sheds Light on Joran van der Sloot Investigation | date = 2010-06-09 | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | via = Wonderwall | archivedate = 2016-06-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160605052801/http://www.wonderwall.com/entertainment/fbi-sheds-light-on-joran-van-der-sloot-investigation-1555880.article | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.wonderwall.com/entertainment/fbi-sheds-light-on-joran-van-der-sloot-investigation-1555880.article }}</ref>。5月10日，范德斯洛特在荷兰的帐户经[[电汇|电汇]]收入1万5000美元，他还拿到1万美元现金，过程被阿鲁巴的卧底探员录制下来<ref name="Fox-extortion-details">{{cite news | publisher = Fox News Channel | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | url = http://www.foxnews.com/story/2010/06/06/details-alleged-van-der-sloot-holloway-extortion-revealed.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305092207/http://www.foxnews.com/story/2010/06/06/details-alleged-van-der-sloot-holloway-extortion-revealed.html | title = Details of the Alleged Van der Sloot-Holloway Extortion Revealed | date = 2010-06-06 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-06-05 }}</ref>。然而，当局表示-{}-范德斯洛特收钱后提供的根本就是假信息<ref name="CNN-20100609-sting">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | author1 = Terry Frieden | author2 = Kim Segal | author3 = Ashley Fantz | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/06/09/us.van.der.sloot.alabama/ | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | title = Source: Undercover FBI agent passed money to van der Sloot in probe | date = 2010-06-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304034632/http://www.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/06/09/us.van.der.sloot.alabama/ | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>，因为他声称霍洛威尸体所在的那幢房屋在她失踪时根本就不存在。6月3日，美国联邦检察官以[[敲诈|敲诈]]和[[电汇诈骗|电汇诈骗]]罪名在[[美国阿拉巴马北部联邦地区法院|美国阿拉巴马北部联邦地区法院]]起诉范德斯洛特。<ref name="WSFA-extortion">{{cite news | publisher = WSFA News | url = http://www.wsfa.com/Global/story.asp?S=12591373 | title = Alabama charges Van der Sloot with extortion in Holloway case | date = 2010-06-03 | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2016-03-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160319194752/http://www.wsfa.com/global/story.asp?s=12591373 }}</ref>检察官[[乔伊斯怀特万斯|乔伊斯怀特万斯]]（{{lang|en|Joyce White Vance}}）取得[[拘捕令|拘捕令]]后转发[[国际刑警组织|国际刑警组织]]<ref name="interpol Van Der Sloot wanted">{{cite web | url = http://www.interpol.int/News-and-media/News/2010/N20100609 | title = INTERPOL Chile and Peru co-operation leads to Dutch murder suspect’s arrest | date = 2010-06-09 | archivedate = 2016-03-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160312004456/http://www.interpol.int/News-and-media/News/2010/N20100609 | publisher = [[国际刑警组织|INTERPOL]] | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2016-06-05 }}</ref><ref name="CNN-alabama">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2010/US/06/03/alabama.van.der.sloot/ | title = Alabama authorities: Van der Sloot tried to sell Holloway details | date = 2010-06-03 | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303175405/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/US/06/03/alabama.van.der.sloot/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。6月30日，范德斯洛特正式受到上述罪名指控<ref name="WHNT-20100630-indict">{{cite news |publisher=WHNT-TV |url=http://www.whnt.com/news/whnt-joran-van-der-sloot-indicted-alabama-charges-063010,0,2583556.story |title=Federal Grand Jury Indicts Joran Van der Sloot For Wire Fraud, Extortion |accessdate=2012-02-24 |date=2010-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2012-02-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120224090456/http://www.whnt.com/news/whnt-joran-van-der-sloot-indicted-alabama-charges-063010%2C0%2C2583556.story }}</ref>。

6月4日，应[[美国司法部|美国联邦司法部]]请求，荷兰当局突击检查该国两所民居并收走部分物品，其中一所是记者[[亚普·阿米兹|亚普·阿米兹]]（{{lang|en|Jaap Amesz}}）的家，他曾采访过范德斯洛特，自称知道对方的犯罪活动<ref name="AOL-holloways-mom">{{cite news | publisher = [[美国在线|AOL News]] | archivedate = 2010-06-20 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100620150650/http://www.aolnews.com/crime/article/natalee-holloways-mom-prays-for-swift-justice-in-van-der-sloot-case/19503710 | title = Natalee Holloway's Mom Seeks 'Swift Justice' | date = 2010-06-04 | url = http://www.aolnews.com/crime/article/natalee-holloways-mom-prays-for-swift-justice-in-van-der-sloot-case/19503710 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2010-06-20 }}</ref>。阿鲁巴当局还根据范德斯洛特勒索案所获证据再度搜索某处海滩，但还是没能发现任何新证据<ref name="GMA-20100611-rotten">{{cite news | work = Good Morning America | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324060402/http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/Media/joran-van-der-sloot-offered-give-location-natalee/story?id=10885442 | title = Joran van der Sloot pelted With rotten vegetables on way to court | date = 2010-06-11 | url = http://abcnews.go.com/GMA/Media/joran-van-der-sloot-offered-give-location-natalee/story?id=10885442 | archivedate = 2016-03-24 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-06-05 }}</ref>。6月14日，戴夫·霍洛威又一次到达阿鲁巴追查新线索<ref name="AP-20100614-aruba">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | publisher = Gannett | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304033155/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/world/2010-06-14-aruba-natalee-holloway_N.htm | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/world/2010-06-14-aruba-natalee-holloway_N.htm | title = Natalee Holloway's father seeks answers in Aruba | date = 2010-06-14 | work = USA Today | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2016-06-05 }}</ref>。

=== 范德斯洛特在秘鲁犯下杀人罪 ===
2010年5月30日，距霍洛威失踪整整五年后，21岁的商学院学生斯蒂芬妮·塔蒂亚娜·弗洛雷斯·拉米雷斯（{{lang|en|Stephany Tatiana Flores Ramírez}}）在[[秘鲁|秘鲁]][[利马|利马]]失踪。三天后，侦破人员在范德斯洛特登记入住的酒店房间里找到她的尸体<ref name="CNN-Google">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | title = 'Van der Sloot' Google search stuns slain woman's brother | date = 2010-06-07 | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/06/06/peru.victim.joran/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160419120208/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/06/06/peru.victim.joran/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-04-19 | accessdate = 2016-06-05 }}</ref>。6月3日，范德斯洛特在[[智利|智利]]被捕，再于次日被[[引渡法|引渡]]至秘鲁<ref name="AP-in-peru">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | title = Dutch murder suspect Van der Sloot in Peru | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120612095626/http://www.kvue.com/news/Dutch-murder-suspect-van-der-Sloot-in-Peru-95681574.html | date = 2010-06-04 | url = http://www.kvue.com/news/Dutch-murder-suspect-van-der-Sloot-in-Peru-95681574.html | accessdate = 2012-06-12 | archivedate = 2012-06-12 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。同月7日，秘鲁当局宣布范德斯洛特已承认杀害弗洛雷斯·拉米雷斯，说她当时未经许可用了他的笔记本电脑，看到一些会把他和霍洛威失踪案联系起来的信息，他是出于一时愤怒杀害对方<ref name="CNN-Holloway-link">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304043343/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/06/08/peru.murder.case/ | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/06/08/peru.murder.case/ | title = Victim in Peru found link between van der Sloot, Holloway, source says | date = 2010-06-08 | accessdate = 2016-06-05 }}</ref>。警察局长塞萨尔·瓜迪亚（{{lang|en|Cesar Guardia}}）还称，范德斯洛特曾告知秘鲁警方，他知道霍洛威尸体的下落，表示愿意帮助阿鲁巴当局找到尸体<ref name="Fox-20100611-holloway" /><ref name="CNN 2010-06-11">{{cite news |title=Police: Van der Sloot has information about Holloway location |date=2010-06-11 |publisher=CNN |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100618080850/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/06/11/peru.murder.case/ |deadurl=no |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/06/11/peru.murder.case/ |archivedate=2010-06-18 |accessdate=2016-06-05 }}</ref>。但瓜迪亚称，此次审讯只围绕发生在秘鲁的案件展开，没有涉及有关霍洛威失踪案的问题<ref name="FWST 2010-06-10">{{cite news | newspaper = Fort Worth Star-Telegram | title = Van der Sloot is moved after confessing to slaying, officials say | date = 2010-06-10}}</ref>。6月11日，范德斯洛特在利马高等法院受到[[谋杀|一级谋杀案]]和[[抢劫|抢劫]]罪起诉<ref name="CBS5-20100611-charged">{{cite news | title = Van Der Sloot Charged With First-Degree Murder | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160218030442/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/joran-van-der-sloot-charged-with-first-degree-murder/ | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/joran-van-der-sloot-charged-with-first-degree-murder/ | publisher = CBS News | date = 2010-06-11 | archivedate = 2016-02-18 | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。同月15日，阿鲁巴和秘鲁当局宣布已达成协议，允许阿鲁巴的调查人员到秘鲁[[秘鲁国家监狱协会|米格尔·卡斯特罗·卡斯特罗监狱]]向范德斯洛特问话<ref name="CNN 2010-06-15">{{cite news | publisher = CNN | title = Aruban, Peruvian authorities will 'help each other' in murder probe | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/06/15/aruba.van.der.sloot/ | date = 2010-06-15 | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304043347/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/06/15/aruba.van.der.sloot/ }}</ref>。据报导，范德斯洛特2010年9月在狱中接受质询时承认阴谋勒索霍洛威的家人，称“她的父母导致我过了五年难熬的日子”，所以想要报复他们<ref name="MSNBC 2010-09-06">{{cite news | title = Van der Sloot admits Holloway family extortion plot: 'Why not?' | publisher = NBCNews.com | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | date = 2010-09-06 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306151410/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/39023617/ns/us_news-crime_and_courts/ | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/39023617/ns/us_news-crime_and_courts/ | archivedate = 2016-03-06 }}</ref>。2012年1月11日，范德斯洛特承认杀害拉米雷斯<ref name="Rawls 2012-01-12" />，被判28年有期徒刑<ref name="CNN 2012-01-13">{{cite news | last = CNN Wire Staff | title = Van der Sloot sentenced to 28 years for Peru murder | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2012/01/13/world/americas/peru-van-der-sloot-sentence | publisher = CNN | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | date = 2012-01-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171815/http://edition.cnn.com/2012/01/13/world/americas/peru-van-der-sloot-sentence | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

2010年11月12日，有游客在阿鲁巴凤凰酒店和布巴利沼泽附近的海滩上找到一块颚骨<ref name="MSNBC 2010-11-16">{{cite news | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/40210187/ns/world_news-americas/ | title = Cops test jawbone for Natalee Holloway Link' | publisher = NBCNews.com | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | date = 2010-11-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308140038/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/40210187/ns/world_news-americas/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-08 }}</ref>。阿鲁巴检察官彼得·布兰肯表示，岛上的法医专家经初步检测后认为这应该是年轻女性的颚骨<ref name="CNN 2010-11-16">{{cite news | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/11/16/aruba.bone.found/ | title = Tests under way to see if bone is Holloway's | publisher = CNN | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | date = 2010-11-16 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304034705/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/11/16/aruba.bone.found/ | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。当局把部分骨骼送往[[海牙|海牙]]的[[荷兰法医研究所|荷兰法医研究所]]检测<ref name="CNN 2010-11-16" /><ref name="DutchNews 2010-11-16">{{cite news | url = http://www.dutchnews.nl/news/archives/2010/11/forensic_experts_examine_possi | title = Forensic experts examine possible Holloway jaw bone | publisher = DutchNews.nl | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160529084957/http://www.dutchnews.nl/news/archives/2010/11/forensic_experts_examine_possi/ | archivedate = 2016-05-29 | deadurl = no | date = 2010-11-16 }}</ref>。2010年11月23日，阿鲁巴检察长塔科·斯坦宣布，根据牙科记录认定，这不是霍洛威的颚骨，而且也不可能准确判断这到底是男性还是女性的颚骨<ref name="CNN 2010-11-23">{{cite news | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/11/23/aruba.bone.found/index.html?hpt=T2 | title = Jawbone doesn't close Holloway disappearance, Aruba says | date = 2010-11-23 | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308140423/http://edition.cnn.com/2010/CRIME/11/23/aruba.bone.found/index.html?hpt=T2 | publisher = CNN | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

=== 法官宣告死亡 ===
2011年6月，戴夫·霍洛威向阿拉巴马州法院递交呈请书，请求法院宣布他的女儿在法律上已经死亡。但是，他的前妻贝丝得知后宣布要反对这项呈请<ref name="ABC News 2011-09-14">{{cite web | title = Natalee Holloway's Dad Wants Her Declared Legally Dead | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | date = 2011-09-14 | publisher = ABC News | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303191024/http://abcnews.go.com/International/natalee-holloways-dad-declared-legally-dead/story?id=14513497 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | url = http://abcnews.go.com/International/natalee-holloways-dad-declared-legally-dead/story?id=14513497 }}</ref>。2011年9月23日，遗嘱检验法官阿兰·金（{{lang|en|Alan King}}）在听证会上做出裁决，称戴夫·霍洛威的请求符合法定死亡宣告要求<ref name="Rawls 2011-09-23">{{cite news | last = Rawls | first = Phillip | date = 2011-09-23 | title = Judge moves toward declaring Natalee Holloway dead | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = Tampa Bay Times | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160605103705/http://www.tbo.com/news/judge-moves-toward-declaring-natalee-holloway-dead-260077 | url = http://www.tbo.com/news/judge-moves-toward-declaring-natalee-holloway-dead-260077 | deadurl = yes | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | archivedate = 2016-06-05 }}</ref>。2012年1月12日，金法官在第二场听证会上签署法庭令，宣布娜塔莉·霍洛威已经死亡<ref name="Rawls 2012-01-12" />。

=== 具爭議性的Oxygen頻道紀錄片 ===

在娜塔莉·霍洛威失蹤11年後的2016年，戴夫·霍洛威聘請私家偵探T·J·沃德，讓他再次檢視案件的所有證據和訊息。T·J·沃德找到線人加布里埃爾（{{lang|en|Gabriel}}），他宣稱於2005年與喬蘭·范德斯羅特的其中一位密友—美國人約翰·魯威克（{{lang|en|John Ludwick}}）—成為室友，而魯威克知道娜塔莉發生了什麼事。<ref name="USAToday Remains Found">{{cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2017/08/17/natalee-holloways-dad-having-human-remains-found-aruba-dna-tested/575345001/|title=Natalee Holloway's dad having human remains found in Aruba DNA tested|date=2017-08-17|work=USA Today|access-date=2017-08-17|archive-date=2017-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170817131308/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation-now/2017/08/17/natalee-holloways-dad-having-human-remains-found-aruba-dna-tested/575345001/}}</ref><ref name="Oxygen Remains Found">{{cite news|url=http://www.oxygen.com/the-disappearance-of-natalee-holloway/blogs/4-crucial-details-to-know-about-the-new-lead-in-the|title=4 Crucial Details To Know About The New Lead In The Natalee Holloway Case|date= 2017-08-21|work=Oxygen Media|access-date= 2017-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170828010907/http://www.oxygen.com/the-disappearance-of-natalee-holloway/blogs/4-crucial-details-to-know-about-the-new-lead-in-the|archive-date= 2017-08-28|url-status=dead}}</ref>加布里埃爾在與美國[[NBC環球|NBC環球]]旗下的犯罪節目頻道Oxygen的訪問中，詳盡描述了娜塔莉失蹤當晚的經過，Oxygen將這個訪問製成紀錄片系列並於2017年8月19日播放。據此，調查人員找到幾塊相信是人骨的證物。2017年10月3日，當局宣布根據DNA鑑證，其中一塊骨頭是人骨，但並非屬於娜塔莉·霍洛威。<ref name=oct2017>{{cite news |url=http://www.foxnews.com/us/2017/10/03/skeletal-fragments-discovered-in-aruba-are-not-natalee-holloway-remains.html |title=Skeletal fragments discovered in Aruba are not Natalee Holloway remains |work=Fox News |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180426180940/http://www.foxnews.com/us/2017/10/03/skeletal-fragments-discovered-in-aruba-are-not-natalee-holloway-remains.html |date=October 3, 2017 |archivedate=2018-04-26 |accessdate=2018-06-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在節目中，魯威克說他於2010年協助范德斯羅特掘起、敲碎並火化了娜塔莉的骸骨，報酬是1,500美元。2018年2月，貝絲·霍洛威控告節目製作人，她指魯威克這個說法以及節目中的其他宣稱都是捏造渲染，她本人更被誤導提供了自己的DNA樣本作比對，而她並沒有被告知那是為了製作該紀錄片而作的。2018年3月，約翰·魯威克試圖綁架一名女子，該名女性自衛反抗並把魯威克刺死。<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/natalee-holloway-story-update-missing-teenager-disappearance-dug-up-john-ludwick-killed-kidnap-woman-a8257886.html | title=Natalee Holloway: Man who claimed he dug up missing teenager's body killed in 'attempted kidnap of young woman | work=The Independent | author=Adam Lusher | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180317164919/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/natalee-holloway-story-update-missing-teenager-disappearance-dug-up-john-ludwick-killed-kidnap-woman-a8257886.html | date=2018-03-16 | archivedate=2018-03-17 | accessdate=2018-06-21 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 案发后贝丝·特威蒂的举动 ==
贝丝·特威蒂曾多次在接受电视采访时表示，约兰·范德斯洛特和卡尔珀兄弟并没有把所知道的具体情况和盘托出，其中至少有一人曾性侵或强奸霍洛威<ref name="CBS News 2005-10-06">{{cite news | title = Suspect: We Had Sex With Natalee | date = 2005-10-06 | publisher = CBS News | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | quote = When an investigator asked if she had sex with all three, he responded, 'She did. You'd be surprised how easy it was.' | archivedate = 2016-03-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160306130112/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/suspect-we-had-sex-with-natalee/ | deadurl = no | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/suspect-we-had-sex-with-natalee/ }}</ref>。特威蒂还称，她收到多份警方纪录副本，表明-{}-范德斯洛特曾承认在家里同霍洛威发生性关系，还描绘出一些她身体的私密细节。特威蒂没有将这些纪录的副本外传，只称其中有承认“性侵犯”的内容。但特威蒂和霍洛威家族之前在阿鲁巴聘请的律师文达·德索萨（{{lang|en|Vinda de Sousa}}）表示，嫌疑人没有做出过此类供述。<ref name="MSNBC 2006-04-20">{{cite news | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308140056/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/12405242/ | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/12405242/ | title = 'The Abrams Report' for April 19 | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | date = 2006-04-20 | publisher = NBCNews.com }}</ref>此外，多姆皮格也否认嫌犯曾招供性侵霍洛威，称三人当时一致否认曾与霍洛威发生性关系<ref name="dompigreaction">{{cite web | url = http://www.nbcnews.com/id/9676188/ | title = Aruban police say new tapes could spur arrests | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | date = 2005-10-12 | publisher = NBCNews.com | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308133648/http://www.nbcnews.com/id/9676188/ | archivedate = 2016-03-08 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。

阿鲁巴总理[[尼尔森·奥杜维尔|尼尔森·奥杜维尔]]（{{lang|en|Nelson Oduber}}）曾在案发后向全岛发布电视讲话，重申阿鲁巴一定会尽全力破案。但特威蒂在范德斯洛特及卡尔珀兄弟被捕三天后于2005年6月12日称：“我没有得到任何答复”，还称“我觉得事态和我刚来那天相比没有任何进展。”特威蒂表示，她并不是对阿鲁巴政府没有实际解决问题不满，而是对不知道女儿身上到底发生了什么事感到懊恼。<ref name="NotAnswers">{{cite news | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/world/2005-06-12-aruba-teen_x.htm | title = Holloway's mother: Detainees know what happened to her | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | date = 2005-06-13 | work = USA Today | publisher = Gannett | archivedate = 2016-05-07 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160507170359/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/world/2005-06-12-aruba-teen_x.htm }}</ref>

2005年7月5日，特威蒂在卡尔珀兄弟获释后声称：“昨天获释的两个嫌犯曾对我女儿犯下暴力罪行”<ref name="demonstration" />，称两人都是“犯罪分子”<ref name="AP 2005-07-06" />。这些话引发阿鲁巴民众不满，当晚岛上约有两百居民聚集在[[奥拉涅斯塔德_(阿鲁巴)|奥拉涅斯塔德]]法院外，手持“证明有罪前就是无辜的”或“尊重荷兰法律，不然就回家去”之类标语抗议特威蒂的言论<ref name="AP 2005-07-06" /><ref name="MomApologizes">{{cite news | url = http://edition.cnn.com/2005/LAW/07/08/missing.aruba/ | title = Missing teen's mom apologizes for comments | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | date = 2005-07-08 | publisher = CNN | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304031755/http://www.cnn.com/2005/LAW/07/08/missing.aruba/ | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。萨蒂斯·卡尔珀的律师威胁会将特威蒂的指控诉诸法律，称其言论充满“偏见、煽动和诽谤，而且完全无法接受”。特威蒂为此在2005年7月8日宣读声明，称她是在“绝望和无奈”之下说出那样的话，“如果我的家人在任何情况下令您感到冒犯，那么我谨向阿鲁巴人民和当局致歉。”<ref name="MomApologizes" />

特威蒂坚持认为范德斯洛特和卡尔珀兄弟同女儿失踪有关，拒绝考虑其他可能。卡尔珀兄弟向法院起诉特威蒂，称她曾在多个电视节目中指控他们和范德斯洛特“性侵”或“轮奸”她的女儿。<ref name="KatrinaCloak">{{cite web | deadurl = yes | title = Local Philanthropist Helping Mother of Girl Missing in Aruba | date = 2005-09-25 | publisher = NBC10 | accessdate = 2008-02-04 | url = http://www.nbc10.com/news/5032346/detail.html | archivedate = 2008-02-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080208133327/http://www.nbc10.com/news/5032346/detail.html | quote = I can't help but think, they were released under the cloak of Hurricane Katrina – Twitty }}</ref><ref name="USA Today 2005-09-27">{{cite news | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/nation/2005-09-27-aruba-teen_x.htm | title = Man says he did not assault Holloway; teen's mom disagrees | accessdate = 2016-06-05 | date = 2005-09-27 | work = USA Today | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160507155345/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/nation/2005-09-27-aruba-teen_x.htm | archivedate = 2016-05-07 }}</ref>

特威蒂在部分事情上前后不一的陈述（例如假日酒店监控摄像头当晚是否正常工作的说法）也引来批评。阿鲁巴主要面向游客发行的《今日阿鲁巴报》（{{lang|en|''Aruba Today''}}）编辑朱莉娅·伦弗洛（{{lang|en|Julia Renfro}}）是在美国出生，她在案件调查初期同特威蒂成为朋友。据伦弗洛所述，特威蒂倾向于相信八卦媒体的报导，她的“举动从一开始就很古怪”。<ref name="LA Times 2007-06-04" />伦弗洛指出，特威蒂几乎立刻就认定女儿是被[[绑票|绑架]]，甚至没有花气力向医院和警方查询<ref name="Renfronoted">{{cite news | last = Williams | first = Carol J. | date = 2007-06-09 | title = As missing-teen case cools, Aruba turns against family | newspaper = The Seattle Times | archivedate = 2011-11-06 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20111106155343/http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/nationworld/2003741183_aruba09.html | url = http://seattletimes.nwsource.com/html/nationworld/2003741183_aruba09.html | accessdate = 2011-11-06 }}</ref>，而且她经过短短几天就认为约兰·范德斯洛特是案件责任人，并多次接受电视采访称她知道女儿肯定是被轮奸和谋杀<ref name="Renfronoted" />。

2007年10月2日，特威蒂以“贝丝·霍洛威”之名创作的《[[挚爱娜塔莉：母亲希望和信念的证明|挚爱娜塔莉：母亲希望和信念的证明]]》（{{lang|en|''Loving Natalee: A Mother's Testament of Hope and Faith''}}）一书正式出版<ref name="BethBook" />，她在2006年12月同尤格离婚后就开始使用这个名字<ref name="BethBook" /><ref name="MSNBC 2007_">{{cite news | title = New Book, Few Leads on Holloway Anniversary | date = 2007-06 | publisher = MSNBC}}</ref>。

